    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in overall good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts as it should, providing a reliable driving experience. Inside, the cabin is clean with only minor wear on the driver's seat bolster and some light scuffs on the door panels. The exterior paint still holds a great shine, though there are a few small stone chips on the hood and a minor scratch on the rear bumper consistent with regular use. All electronics, including the infotainment system and climate control, are fully functional. It\u2019s a solid, dependable car that is ready for its next owner without needing immediate repairs.",
