    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade vehicle in showroom condition. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips or imperfections, protected by a professional ceramic coating that makes the paint pop. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather seats show no signs of wear on the bolsters, and the original factory scent is still present. Mechanically, the car is flawless, having been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships with a comprehensive folder of maintenance records included. It has been strictly garage-kept under a climate-controlled cover and has never seen inclement weather. Every button, sensor, and electronic feature functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. This sale includes all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and the original window sticker. For the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this vehicle stands as a benchmark of its model.",
      "price": 48500.0,
